    "description": "API for managing CTN (Connecting the Netherlands) Association Register - A comprehensive system for managing legal entities, member applications, endpoint registrations, and BVAD token management.\n\n## API Versioning\n\nThis API uses URL path versioning (e.g., `/api/v1/`, `/api/v2/`). All responses include version headers:\n\n- `API-Version`: Current API version\n- `Deprecation`: Date when version was deprecated (RFC 8594)\n- `Sunset`: Date when version will be sunset (RFC 8594)\n- `Link`: Migration guide URL (rel=\"deprecation\")\n\n**Current Version:** v1\n**Status:** Active\n\n**Migration Guide:** See [API Versioning Strategy](https://docs.ctn.cloud/api/versioning) for details.\n\n**Deprecation Policy:** Previous versions are supported for 12 months after a new major version release. After sunset, deprecated versions return HTTP 410 Gone.",
